For Data Science Process, the raw data must pass through Data Science Categories. Which are 
    
    1. Data Management.
    2. Data Integration and Transformation.
    3. Data Visualization.
    4. Model Building.
    5. Model Deployment.
    6. Model Monitoring and Assessment.
    
These Process are Supported by tools and methods which are 

    1. Code Asset Management.
    2. Data Asset Management.
    3. Development Environment.
    4. Execution Environment.
    
There are tools available in the market to do all these process in one workspace like Fully Integrated Visual Tools.
